<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='437488' id='t-437488'>So with sound as my new art medium,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='440167' id='t-440167'>I delved into the world of music.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='443089' id='t-443089'>And I was surprised to see
